===================
pyomo.extras README
===================

The Pyomo software project integrates a variety of Python
optimization-related packages.  Pyomo supports a diverse set of
optimization capabilities that can be used formulate and analyze
optimization applications.  

This is an extension package that includes a variety of Python
packages that Pyomo optionally leverages.
